{"tid":2272114,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"311十週年 富士電視台以東北災區為舞台製作3套動畫作品","createTime":"2020-11-05T01:54:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T02:19:39.000Z","uid":4618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0dc7583f19952564b3cd5e0494b9869402206077","tid":2272114,"uid":4618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T01:54:39.000Z","msg":"震災から10年&hellip;フジテレビが被災地を舞台にしたアニメ3作品を制作<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cinematoday.jp/news/N0119665.amp.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cinematoday.jp%2Fnews%2FN0119665.amp.html&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4Ftf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=4d67204e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cinematoday.jp/news/N0119665.amp.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WswX1hy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWswX1hy.jpg&h=517cd1d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一套係TV動畫《バクテン!!》，男子體操部題材，舞台係宮城縣<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/bakuten_pr/status/1324064118182203392?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbakuten_pr%2Fstatus%2F1324064118182203392%3Fs%3D21&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4Ftf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=bd6c2fa5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbakuten_pr%2Fstatus%2F1324064118182203392%3Fs%3D21&h=2f1a1d2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/bakuten_pr/status/1324064118182203392?s=21</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BP3O70d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBP3O70d.jpg&h=2a5b4efa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.animatetimes.com/news/details.php?id=1604479827&amp;pagemode=amp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.animatetimes.com%2Fnews%2Fdetails.php%3Fid%3D1604479827%26pagemode%3Damp&d=GnUrxgUttZjT4wJVsekm4Ftf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=8ab50688\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.animatetimes.com/news/details.php?id=1604479827&amp;pagemode=amp</a><br />\n<br />\n